[28/10/2019 02:30:24] <font color="#ffffff">Sukarno,</font>
[28/10/2019 02:30:24] <font color="#ffffff">un déspota ilustrado,</font>
[28/10/2019 02:30:27] <font color="#ffffff">sigue considerado como</font>
